##### Connection to Hypothesis (Figure 1):
While not directly linked to my hypothesis, it helps contextualize why researching this issue is timely given the increase in U.S. interventions over time—my figure confers with research done in the field already. It sets the foundation for whether heightened intervention correlates with unintended consequences, such as civilian harm and the rise in extremist groups.


